<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/249968-how-did-anyone-like-the-entire-bride">How did anyone like the entire Bride Quartet series? As a writer, Nora Roberts is one of the top authors in this genre and I love her wording. It&#39;s not so easy to come up with fresh ways of the saying, &quot;She smiled at him,&quot; over and over again, but Nora can. She&#39;s a good study in wordsmithing.</a>
</div>
