<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I enjoyed her Parker character the most. She was complicated and tough with a veneer that would be hard for a schmoozer to get past. All four books we<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I enjoyed her Parker character the most. She was complicated and tough with a veneer that would be hard for a schmoozer to get past. All four books were fun reads.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
